Pure Python interface for the GittiGidiyor RESTLIKE API.

For linux;
  - sudo aptitude install python-httplib2 python-simplejson python-setuptools

For MAC OSX users;
  - Download the latest httplib2 package from the link below;
    * wget -c http://httplib2.googlecode.com/files/httplib2-0.6.0.zip
    * unzip httplib2-0.6.0.zip
    * cd httplib2-0.6.0
    * sudo python setup.py install

 - Download the latest simplejson library from the link below.
   * wget -c http://pypi.python.org/packages/source/s/simplejson/simplejson-2.1.1.tar.gz#md5=0bbe3a2e5e4cac040013733aca159d89
   * tar zxvf simplejson-2.1.1.tar.gz
   * cd simplejson-2.1.1
   * sudo python setup.py install
